{"tid":778361,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"公佈18-19最新世界四大聯賽排名","createTime":"2018-08-13T15:35:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T12:56:00.000Z","uid":87155,"like":8,"dislike":80,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"45eef76b3552f1d8872f3eb45b54454dd65701c3","tid":778361,"uid":87155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:35:31.000Z","msg":"排名分先後<br />\n1.西甲<br />\n2.意甲<br />\n3.英超<br />\n4.法甲=德甲<br />\n<br />\n原因 ：歐聯3連霸既皇馬已經解釋左第一<br />\n世一c朗去埋意大利幫意甲復興 加上羅馬 拿玻里翻身  跳升第二 <br />\n英超雖然群雄逐鹿 有big 6之名 但實則都係曼城一隊玩哂但都要出去歐聯比人屈機 隊英人係英超咁屈出去世界盃就on9仔咁 例子詳見250 可見成隊英超都係圍威喂 <br />\n法甲有球王麥巴比加尼馬 幫法甲帶高一個lv 所以同德甲一撚樣1人聯賽唔洗爭<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1695f80f09b532fa209d84ff273fbe80a002377e","tid":778361,"uid":52571,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:36:55.000Z","msg":"笑左THX"},{"pid":"7fff7a4c45939fac21c9a63370a948e8be83efa4","tid":778361,"uid":56240,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:42:56.000Z","msg":"玩具足球<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07588242b71a32c09d09fe3dfb9ba93442d8d34","tid":778361,"uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:44:16.000Z","msg":"樓主259"},{"pid":"cbea8f55086550facc1979e52c63daa179ae5dd0","tid":778361,"uid":58163,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:45:16.000Z","msg":"樓主做晒暑期作業未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183f998625507f023459d21253a3b5deffea0c5b","tid":778361,"uid":144063,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-13T15:45:40.000Z","msg":"英超BIG 6出到歐洲成碌柒咁 走喇"},{"pid":"591785fcbe1a0a043de240e1f68194ab0886b6bf","tid":778361,"uid":38189,"like":39